WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.200
Grow a forest.

00:04.200 --> 00:07.200
Have you ever been to a forest?

00:07.200 --> 00:11.540
Have you ever wanted to save the trees in the forest?

00:11.540 --> 00:16.440
Do you love nature and want to keep forests safe?

00:16.440 --> 00:18.360
Now you can.

00:18.360 --> 00:20.240
Buy a tree.

00:20.240 --> 00:28.080
It is the perfect birthday or wedding present for someone in your family or for a friend.

00:28.080 --> 00:34.920
A tree is also something special for a festival or a new baby.

00:34.920 --> 00:43.640
Your tree will help our world and will last longer than toys, clothes or computers.

00:43.640 --> 00:46.640
The world needs more trees.

00:46.640 --> 00:48.480
Buy one today.

00:48.480 --> 00:53.920
Watch it grow bigger and feel proud.

00:53.920 --> 01:02.080
The Grow a Forest gift is part of an exciting plan to make our world greener.

01:02.080 --> 01:06.560
And every gift helps to protect our world.

01:06.560 --> 01:08.520
It is easy.

01:08.520 --> 01:16.160
Buy a Grow a Forest gift today and choose your forest and your tree.

01:16.160 --> 01:20.760
We will take it and put it in the earth for you.

01:20.760 --> 01:27.400
Then we will send a gift box from you to your family or friend.

01:27.400 --> 01:35.640
In your gift box there will be a map of the forest, a photo of your tree.

01:35.640 --> 01:44.840
A pair of Grow a Forest gloves, a card with your message to your family or friend.

01:44.840 --> 01:47.640
Grow a tree near you.

